  completionMessage: Mandate ab measurable public work mein badla. Har shortcut ka
    hisaab save ho chuka hai.
  chapterNumber: 8
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 8 / PEHLE 100 DIN
  introMessage: Election jeetna shuruaat thi. Ab budget, delivery aur imaandari ka
    public test hai.
